data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
Elevate your desktop experience by personalizing it with a theme based on your most cherished image. Using your wallpaper - whether a photo, art, or favorite image - WallStudio analyzes the image and extracts colors form it to create a full Windows theme.
How do you do it? - Choose your image - simply choose a wallpaper or an image that inspires you - Preview your colors - see how WallStudio interprets the tones in your selected image - Let WallStudio create your new desktop style automatically
Entirely Offline - Everything happens on your machine. WallStudio does not use the internet or rely on cloud services, or AI for everything it uses is on your machine. Everything runs quickly, efficiently, and under your control.
With WallStudio, your wallpaper is more than your desktop's background - it's the foundation for how your desktop will look and feel. Every color, every accent, every highlighted color is pulled directly from your wallpaper photo, and your computer gets a style that is all your own.

data.name: label11.Text
data.value: Fine-tune the way in which WallStudio creates your theme by choosing your own preferences below. These options will help WallStudio create a better look that feels just right for your own desktop look.

data.name: label12.Text
data.value: Check this box if you want WallStudio to base all accent colors on the most dominant color from your wallpaper. It's a harmonious, minimalist look. Leave it unchecked for a full palette of complementary colors for a richer, more varied theme.
